29:57.779 --> 30:00.496
So whoever did this must've
been high or half asleep.

30:00.498 --> 30:02.114
I don't care.

30:05.620 --> 30:07.169
Okay.

30:07.171 --> 30:08.921
You know what? Just go...
go... go get it fixed.

30:08.923 --> 30:10.706
I don't care how you do
it. Just get it fixed.

30:10.708 --> 30:11.924
- Hey, hey.
- Thank you.

30:11.926 --> 30:13.459
Uh, what was that all about?

30:13.461 --> 30:15.428
Ah, some people just need to
be reminded of their power.

30:15.430 --> 30:17.129
If we're gonna make that spin-off money,

30:17.131 --> 30:19.532
she's got to come through.

30:19.534 --> 30:20.933
Oh.

30:20.935 --> 30:23.135
Hey, why don't you, uh...

30:23.137 --> 30:24.770
Why don't you check her out?

30:24.772 --> 30:26.522
Make sure she got the message.

30:26.524 --> 30:27.807
Okay.

30:29.310 --> 30:32.478
Whew.

30:36.217 --> 30:38.618
Are you okay?

30:39.737 --> 30:43.155
You need to pull your shit together.

30:43.157 --> 30:45.491
Excuse me?

30:45.493 --> 30:47.376
I mean, what is wrong with you?

30:47.378 --> 30:49.078
You used to be like a shark.

30:49.080 --> 30:51.197
Dead eyes, no emotion, no weakness.

30:51.199 --> 30:52.498
- And now look at you.
- I'm sorry.

30:52.500 --> 30:54.133
Are you honestly taking his side?

30:54.135 --> 30:56.135
Because the guy basically
tried to drive me off a cliff.

30:56.137 --> 30:59.087
- Oh, please.
- Holy crap.

30:59.089 --> 31:00.222
- That's a nice ring.
- Yeah.

31:00.224 --> 31:01.390
Yeah.

31:01.392 --> 31:03.142
Chet and I are together now,

31:03.144 --> 31:05.394
so you need to suck it up and do your job.

31:05.396 --> 31:08.731
Yeah, right. Which is what,
exactly? I just want to clarify.

31:08.733 --> 31:10.650
You want me to go into Adam's room
and convince him to do something

31:10.652 --> 31:12.018
that he doesn't want to do, right?

31:12.020 --> 31:15.438
Hell, yeah. Since when is that news?

31:15.440 --> 31:17.189
Okay, how would you like me to do it?

31:17.191 --> 31:18.858
Because you've taken away his winery.

31:18.860 --> 31:21.277
You've turned it into the
"Everlasting" theme park.

31:21.279 --> 31:23.613
And now you're asking me
to get him back on board

31:23.615 --> 31:25.197
with his family, whom he loathes,

31:25.199 --> 31:27.867
and, quite honestly, they're
not crazy about him, either.

31:27.869 --> 31:30.586
Why are you letting Adam
get up all in your vag?

31:30.588 --> 31:33.055
He's a prop, Rachel.

31:34.676 --> 31:39.345
Because maybe I'm just sick
of being a manipulative bitch.

31:39.347 --> 31:40.680
Oh.

31:40.682 --> 31:43.516
Well, let me tell you, sweetheart,

31:43.518 --> 31:46.235
there's no sense fighting that.

31:46.237 --> 31:48.020
That's who we are.

31:51.359 --> 31:53.359
Where are you going?

31:53.361 --> 31:58.030
To be a manipulative bitch.

31:58.032 --> 31:59.332
No means no.

31:59.334 --> 32:01.200
Unless it gets you something you want.

32:01.202 --> 32:02.535
Which is?

32:02.537 --> 32:04.870
Which is your vineyard...
Adam Cromwell Winery.

32:04.872 --> 32:07.340
Fat chance. It's the
"Everlasting" spa and resort now.

32:07.342 --> 32:09.425
Not if you tell Chet you're
gonna do "Royal Love".

32:09.427 --> 32:14.213
But only as "Royal Renovations".

32:14.215 --> 32:15.881
Okay, you cut a deal for the show,

32:15.883 --> 32:17.683
and you insist that they
shoot it at the vineyard.

32:17.685 --> 32:19.268
And we spend the entire
season renovating it

32:19.270 --> 32:20.770
and putting it online,

32:20.772 --> 32:22.772
and you are not gonna commit

32:22.774 --> 32:25.057
unless you get the vineyard
back at the end of the year.

32:25.059 --> 32:26.776
I am talking about the classy cromwell one.

32:26.778 --> 32:29.311
I'm not talking about the
cheesy "Everlasting" one.

32:29.313 --> 32:31.981
And I know that it's
another year of your life,

32:31.983 --> 32:34.900
but at the end of it, you
get everything you want.

32:34.902 --> 32:36.318
Okay, tell me.

32:36.320 --> 32:38.654
Tell me that that's not
gonna impress your father.

32:38.656 --> 32:41.290
It's actually not a bad idea.

32:42.960 --> 32:44.577
But getting married on reality TV?

32:44.579 --> 32:45.911
No, just forget it.

32:45.913 --> 32:48.213
Okay. So you pick Anna.

32:48.315 --> 32:51.917
You propose to her, and
then you just put it off.

32:51.919 --> 32:54.387
So she's your fiancée
for one year. Big deal.

32:54.389 --> 32:56.472
You spend a year of your
life with some beautiful,

32:56.474 --> 32:58.391
smart, sexy woman, and...

32:58.393 --> 33:00.593
You know, when the show's over,

33:00.595 --> 33:03.429
you can... you can do whatever you want.

33:03.431 --> 33:04.814
No marriage.

33:04.816 --> 33:06.515
Not unless you want to.

33:06.517 --> 33:09.068
Okay. So let's say I was interested.

33:09.070 --> 33:11.604
- Mm-hmm.
- What would I need to do?

33:11.606 --> 33:14.740
You just got to get Anna back.

33:16.611 --> 33:19.111
Right.

33:22.116 --> 33:23.749
Madison!

33:23.751 --> 33:25.334
This might qualify as coffee

33:25.336 --> 33:27.753
from whatever fly-over
state you came out of,

33:27.755 --> 33:29.955
but there is no way I'm drinking
this hillbilly monkey piss,

33:29.957 --> 33:33.042
so get your butt down to the
corner and get me a real latte.

33:33.044 --> 33:36.212
I got it.

33:36.214 --> 33:39.465
Word of advice... don't
roll over for Quinn.

33:39.467 --> 33:40.766
She likes the pushback.

33:40.768 --> 33:42.885
I mean, don't... don't be disrespectful,

33:42.887 --> 33:44.887
but get in the ring, have a little fun.

33:44.889 --> 33:48.724
I'm... I'm not scared of
Quinn, if that's what you mean.

33:48.726 --> 33:51.227
Mm. Guess that's why you flinch
every time she talks, huh?

33:51.229 --> 33:54.246
I don't really care how Quinn talks to me.

33:54.248 --> 33:56.782
I have wanted to be in this business

33:56.784 --> 34:00.619
ever since I was a little
girl, and here I am doing it.

34:00.621 --> 34:02.571
Glamorous life of a P.A., huh?

34:02.573 --> 34:04.824
For now.

34:06.744 --> 34:09.545
Hey.

34:09.547 --> 34:11.746
Hey. Hi. Hi.

34:11.748 --> 34:13.165
Um, so...

34:13.167 --> 34:16.418
I broke up with Lizzie.

34:16.820 --> 34:20.306
You what? Are you serious?

34:20.308 --> 34:22.475
Are you gonna... are you okay?

34:22.476 --> 34:24.876
Yeah, Rach, I'm more than okay.

34:24.878 --> 34:27.012
You know, I was just sick
of ignoring the obvious.

34:27.014 --> 34:29.014
What obvious?

34:29.016 --> 34:30.850
It's you.

34:32.687 --> 34:35.571
I just... I don't...

34:35.572 --> 34:38.072
I'm not even sure...

34:49.453 --> 34:52.254
You sure now?

34:53.255 --> 34:54.623
Okay, people... two minutes.

34:54.625 --> 34:56.041
Two minutes.

34:56.043 --> 34:59.879
After wrap, meet me in your truck.

34:59.881 --> 35:03.382
Seriously, it's gonna be good.

35:03.384 --> 35:04.850
- Yeah.
- I promise.

35:10.274 --> 35:12.775
Okay, guys, here we go! Places, please!

35:12.777 --> 35:13.976
And action!

35:13.978 --> 35:15.394
Good evening, and welcome.

35:15.396 --> 35:17.396
