35:17.398 --> 35:19.398
as one of our four remaining contestants

35:19.400 --> 35:21.650
- will be leaving us...
- I'm sorry to interrupt you, uh, Graham...

35:21.652 --> 35:24.069
but there's something, um, I
would like to get off my chest

35:24.071 --> 35:26.205
before the elimination,
if that's all right.

35:26.207 --> 35:29.074
Of course, Adam, yes. What is it?

35:29.076 --> 35:31.911
Uh, Anna, my behavior on our
date today was inexcusable,

35:31.913 --> 35:34.246
