have a moment alone together

35:34.248 --> 35:35.464
before the ceremony.

35:35.466 --> 35:37.750
Yeah, of course.

35:37.752 --> 35:39.919
Okay.

35:39.921 --> 35:41.503
"A" cam, stay with Anna.

35:41.505 --> 35:44.924
And Adam on "B" cam go
wide, please? Thank you.

35:57.905 --> 36:00.072
I am sorry about today.

36:00.074 --> 36:03.192
I was upset, and I wanted you to know

36:03.194 --> 36:05.244
that it had nothing to do with you.

36:05.246 --> 36:08.280
It's, uh...

36:10.084 --> 36:13.953
It's just overwhelming sometimes...

36:13.955 --> 36:15.454
Trying to remember who I am

36:15.456 --> 36:17.923
and what I want in the
middle of all this, and...

36:17.925 --> 36:19.191
It's easy to forget

36:19.193 --> 36:22.461
that I actually have
real feelings and desires.

36:22.463 --> 36:24.713
And what's crazy

36:24.715 --> 36:27.132
is that I know that you
and I have a connection.

36:27.134 --> 36:31.303
And I... I'd really like to
take the time to explore that.

36:31.305 --> 36:32.721
So would I.

36:32.723 --> 36:34.773
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

36:34.775 --> 36:38.777
Let's do that.

36:52.326 --> 36:55.327
Chet, look at this. Look...

36:55.329 --> 36:58.163
Oh. Uh, Chet?

37:36.587 --> 37:38.838
Have you made your choice, Adam?

37:38.840 --> 37:43.126
Yes, I have.

38:01.479 --> 38:03.229
Can't say I'm shocked.

38:03.231 --> 38:06.649
This entire show has been
an obscene waste of my time.

38:10.071 --> 38:11.404
Well...

38:11.406 --> 38:13.956
That's the last of my girls.

38:14.158 --> 38:16.508
- I'm out. Bye
-bye, Jay.

38:16.510 --> 38:17.293
Sorry, buddy.

38:17.295 --> 38:19.462
Bye, Jay.

38:20.882 --> 38:24.500
See you next season, chica.

38:32.060 --> 38:34.344
Mm.

38:34.346 --> 38:38.648
Try not to blow anything up, okay?

39:24.195 --> 39:26.112
- Hey.
- Tell me that one later.

39:26.114 --> 39:27.397
Yeah, okay.

39:27.399 --> 39:29.315
All right. Hey.

39:30.017 --> 39:34.136
Hi. You were right.

39:34.138 --> 39:35.037
Me?

39:35.039 --> 39:37.223
We should get married as soon as we can...

39:37.225 --> 39:38.924
As soon as the papers come through.

39:38.926 --> 39:42.411
Us, Vegas, Elvis impersonator.

39:42.413 --> 39:43.913
Let's do it.

39:43.915 --> 39:46.049
That's amazing. Yes!

39:54.376 --> 39:56.593
Hey.

39:56.595 --> 39:58.879
- Hey.
- Do you need something?

39:58.881 --> 40:00.147
