went really well with Anna.

40:14.099 --> 40:16.516
Yeah. It did. She's... she's lovely.

40:16.518 --> 40:18.435
But we've been on two dates, and what...

40:18.437 --> 40:20.987
We're gonna commit to each
other for an entire year...

40:20.989 --> 40:23.856
- Adam, come on.
- What if I find out she drives me insane?

40:23.958 --> 40:26.725
Or I her. What're we gonna do then?

40:26.727 --> 40:28.811
